      <%= f.hidden_field :person_id, value: session[:id] %>
     <h4><li>Once you confirm the adoption we will share the good news and make sure 
        to get everything ready for your arrival tomorrow! </li><br><br>
        <li>Your fur baby will be ready between
        10:00am - 5:00pm <br></li>
        Address: Please see our Contact Page<br><br>
        <li>New Beginnings Shelter thanks you for saving a life! </h4><br></li>

    <%= f.hidden_field :animal_id, value: @animal.id %>
    <button class="btn btn-success" type="submit">Create Adoption!</button>

    <%end%>
</ul>



